{"tid":1100791,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我以為我想將第一次留俾老公係啱嘅，但男友偷食","createTime":"2019-04-10T15:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T15:59:49.000Z","uid":76105,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37300aa999d031bbbcde61e6ad58874bcc7347de","tid":1100791,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"我今年30歲<br />\n我哋一齊左2年多，上年年尾佢求婚<br />\n我哋計劃今年年尾結婚<br />\n<br />\n佢喺我初戀，我一直覺得自己好幸運，初戀就揾到一個同我一生一世嘅人<br />\n一直無同佢發生關係，就算求左婚都無，因為我想留俾老公，同怕行禮前有bb<br />\n但男朋友無逼過我仲好錫我，對我屋企人都好好<br />\n<br />\n上個月男友突然同我講<br />\n佢原來同我一齊嘅時候除咗揾ex上床，仲有玩交友app識女仔<br />\n其中一個仲去過旅行...我當時以為佢自己去仲好放心<br />\n佢仲帶過女仔上我地裝修緊嘅新居..<br />\n我聽到唔識喊...點解要咁對我...<br />\n上我哋未來嘅家...我一想起就好想喊<br />\n佢係咪同我講緊笑..<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知結唔結婚好..佢喺咁求我原諒<br />\n30歲先散？我怕再揾唔到下一個...<br />\n好迷惘..希望大家口下留情..已經好傷心..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=793706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D793706&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTqix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=7d4d6172\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=793706</a>"},{"pid":"874933c0f311922ca1b7c9230b9db378ecdcdf4b","tid":1100791,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"開錯台添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f677fe1a56068b14df1a6c9685e333ae4983d9","tid":1100791,"uid":199162,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"唔怪得兩年都可以唔扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260dcd2cd99b6a63ffaf522f7b9376f458c6bf4d","tid":1100791,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"你地本身係點一齊"},{"pid":"57b46beecb680ef1b878147f264f2561fb8f7848","tid":1100791,"uid":72085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cit